name: Vanilla Lip Balm
description:
Our Vanilla lip balms are 100% natural leaving your lips perfectly smooth and moisturized; not glossy or greasy.  Beetle bug contains a combination of oils such as coconut oil, jojoba oil and avocado oil.  Cocoa butter and beeswax have been added to solidify the deal.  Beetle balm comes in vanilla flavor; however, there’s a variety of flavors on the horizon so keep a look out! 
Size: 1oz
